deactivate SystemHandle

core -> SystemHandle: spin_once
activate SystemHandle
core <-- SystemHandle: status
deactivate SystemHandle

== to dds ==
other_sh -> Publisher: publish()
activate Publisher
Publisher -> Conversion: soss_to_dds()
